Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上集的LOVELIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接我高二生活的是学校停办的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光辉的高中生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止学校停办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能增加新生的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我建议用现在超流行的学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来展现学校的风采
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像没门！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该好好思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样我也想为学校做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然要去做
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大早上的干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到活动的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和社团没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生可以自由组织活动  学生手册上这么写着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新生欢迎会那一天放学的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个人成立了学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用活动来举行首次演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道做不做得成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  当然要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在还没有登台的水平…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗  就凭你们现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生欢迎会可不是过家家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们三人只是要活动许可而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是社团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会应该没有权力对内容说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要帮她们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管弄多少次都告诉我要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔罗牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔罗牌是这样告诉我的！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别声张学园偶像  先把场地什么的确保好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是和式点心店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我很少吃面包的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在午饭前吃…会胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看了公告板了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要开始做学园偶像了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没想到海未也会参与啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在公告板上贴了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  演唱会的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下不到一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却什么也没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小鸟说可以这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  我设计了下演出服装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的曲线很难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先试着做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧  很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里细长的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要光着腿穿这么短的裙子吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未的腿没那么胖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  减肥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你们两个都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有很多要决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,签名  走在路上时候的变装方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些根本不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组合的名字还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到什么好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人要有什么特征就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的性格也各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就干脆用三个人的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  海未  小鸟  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们叫穗乃果  海未  小鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着像相声演员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未是海  小鸟是空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果是陆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就叫海陆空！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护吧！市民的和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那…  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fad(200,0)}（然后…征集组合名字！）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部交给别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话大家也能提起点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来是歌曲和舞蹈的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里会妨碍到别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也全部被占满了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空教室不能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空教室？  你们要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园偶像的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们？偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似只剩这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有遮阳的地方  下雨时就没法用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要求也不能高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这里不用太在意音量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  努力加油练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从歌声的练习开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练什么歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  穗乃果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在楼上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要吃团子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我必须要减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃团子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上给你倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…减肥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来没有要下定决心努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歌曲方面怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  高一里有个唱得非常好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴也弹得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还会作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我决定明天去问一下她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能帮我们作曲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作词方面就差不多解决了  刚才我们得出了结论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未你啊  初中的时候写过诗什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有叫我们读过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中那时的事现在都害羞得不敢去回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有句话说  偶像要抛弃羞耻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我光制作服装就很吃力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是还有穗乃果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出来的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包子  和松鼠团子  都吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得行不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  只有海未你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能写多少是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未  拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你太狡猾了  小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  演唱会之前的练习表由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习表？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们看起来很开心地在歌唱  但身体一直在动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样呼吸却很流畅  而且保持着笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这需要大量的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果  能做一下俯卧撑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持这样做俯卧撑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在弓道部锻炼过了先不谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃果和小鸟必须要有保持笑容唱歌的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  偶像也挺够呛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来每天早上和傍晚在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和舞蹈唱歌分开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我进行体力训练
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天要两次？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要搞就要搞个像样的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不那样的话  是吸引不了学生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就再来一组
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社是集中了许多祈愿的灵性的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个  既然在用这里的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就顺便参拜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望第一次演唱会可以顺利举行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个人  看来是认真的呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的各位同学  你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是学校偶像  高坂穗乃果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好像完全没听说过我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  穗乃果说的唱歌很好的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你  能来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  我想请你来作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为你只会唱歌  不会作曲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想做而已  那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为了让学校吸引更多的学生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声一定能吸引学生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝  什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟海未一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是正常的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得海未写了那么好的歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  如果作曲完成了  就要大家一起唱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  把A和B作为实数的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须表示为A+BI的形式我们称为复数
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说3I……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在从来没有学校偶像的这个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果试着去做然后失败了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不希望这个学校消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这是真心的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不希望你们想得太简单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能想得太简单了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也不是随便玩玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海未的训练表我都有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此弄得我浑身酸痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也知道你确实很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但学生会长说的话  我们必须正面去接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  连一个月都不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要开演唱会的话  至少也要决定好唱什么歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经没时间再找作曲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得只能唱其他的学校偶像的歌曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会  如果有什么帮得上忙的就说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如照明啊  维持客人的秩序之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多要做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为穗乃果你们为了学校在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同学们也想要为你们打气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,u's？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  应该是缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(750,653)}μ's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肥皂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（日本一家肥皂厂的名字也叫缪斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该用的是神话中登场的女神的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不错  我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  从今天开始我们就是缪斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她们一直在房顶上练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我们学校里也有人搞学校偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花阳  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说西木野同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌很好的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  原来她叫西木野同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  西木野真姬同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找她有事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子她已经回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该在音乐室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐室？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一般不跟大家说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到休息时间就去图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一放学就去音乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加  加油哦  偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想再拜托你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  海未酱一直这么说我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来不听那种音乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一般都是听古典和爵士乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为流行乐太低级了  感觉很轻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种只是随便玩玩的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像节日一样  啪的热闹起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能快乐地唱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  其实还挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你会俯卧撑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当  当然会了  那种小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好厉害  比我做得还多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  别看我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  就这样笑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  当偶像很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着  这是歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着读一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是读一下没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会来问的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时如果你还是说不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会干脆地放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我的回答是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  就让我再听你唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你的歌声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听了那首歌和钢琴弹奏太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想要请你帮我作曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们每天早上和傍晚都在阶梯那里练习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的话  就来玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你的歌声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  还有两个来回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你们要放弃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  海未酱个恶代官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是鬼教官吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还在发育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要不放弃希望就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有变大的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不好意思的话  也可以偷偷去做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我问你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是姐姐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有写收信人的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只写了缪斯
